title: LF Gold player to duo
body: I am past the point of even considering solo que, the amount of dense people I am qued with makes me want to punch a wall..... I do not belong in silver but there isnt much I can do when people give up at 8 minutes or just afk because they cant be bothered... I duo'd with 3 mates but eventually they got plat during duo and now we cant que. As I play alot of league I dont stay same rank as them just add me and we can try afew games
